PRE-INSTALL:

		* Skippy needs NETWM or GNOME WM Specs compliant
		window-manager to works properly

POST-INSTALL:

		* Copy the skippyrc file to your home directory as:
		$ cp skippyrc ~/.skippyrc

		* To start skippy, run:
		$ skippy &

		* To swith between the applications, just press the 
		Scroll_Lock key of your keaybord.

